{"tid":764760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門居民及區議員反對改劃5地建公屋","createTime":"2018-08-02T08:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T10:32:23.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c1abc77204ad2ec6c7bd33f635781835041f6003","tid":764760,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"城規會舉行公聽會，討論屯門分區計劃大綱，涉及改劃5幅用地興建公營房屋。一批屯門居民和區議員到場請願，要求擱置改劃。<br />\n<br />\n屯門區議員葉文斌反對在屯門第16區恒富街空地，改劃興建520個公屋單位。他認為，鄰近的屯門泳池輕鐵站月台出現沉降，加上區內的交通及社區設施負荷大，質疑規劃署為何將計劃提交至城規會討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有屯門區市民反對在恒富街空地，插針式興建兩座屏風樓</strong></span>，形容令地段奇怪和狹窄。<br />\n<br />\n另有屯門區居民指出，屯門公路塞車和西鐵滿客情況嚴重，人口不斷增加，不滿規劃署的報告無提及解決方法。"},{"pid":"28b3ea07c07eac7a971af8bb21335c23d40430b6","tid":764760,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"果頭私樓班友咁撚惡唔俾人起樓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a62ec68a5f379739c53e7ab491d66c733a4d664","tid":764760,"uid":10210,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"隔離係一堆私樓 緊係反對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e6036f23d624e2d81a756f87df8c0d7bb1b34f","tid":764760,"uid":93784,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"源頭減廢 掃走班蝗去大灣區住 根本就冇需要咁插針起公屋"},{"pid":"99e60fc692e724b64c760ce2680997101c66e5dd","tid":764760,"uid":133877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"葉文斌，民建聯及新界社團聯會成員，青年民建聯委員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ce700d6c0c072410185cd9bcee581bfc03cd30","tid":764760,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":